Dialogue: 0,0:00:01.18,0:00:06.24,cloveroprom,,0,0,0,,{\fad(100,200)}watashi ga umareta asa no machi yuki no naka ni umoreta
Dialogue: 0,0:00:07.07,0:00:11.78,cloveroprom,,0,0,0,,{\fad(100,200)}sore wa sore wa chiisai te de aozora wo aoida
Dialogue: 0,0:00:13.09,0:00:18.41,cloveroprom,,0,0,0,,{\fad(100,200)}sanagara mukashi kara yoku shiru tonari no ano ko no you ni
Dialogue: 0,0:00:19.14,0:00:23.27,cloveroprom,,0,0,0,,{\fad(100,200)}katahou no mimitabu de kiku sotsugyou no canon
Dialogue: 0,0:00:23.27,0:00:29.23,cloveroprom,,0,0,0,,{\fad(100,200)}hitori demo daijoubu yo tte mekureteru watashi no story
Dialogue: 0,0:00:29.23,0:00:31.51,cloveroprom,,0,0,0,,{\fad(100,200)}dareka no sei ni shitai yo
Dialogue: 0,0:00:31.51,0:00:35.55,cloveroprom,,0,0,0,,{\fad(100,200)}tsurai naa iya iya
Dialogue: 0,0:00:35.55,0:00:41.05,cloveroprom,,0,0,0,,{\fad(100,200)}kanashikutte naite bakkari itara me ga tokete nakunatta
Dialogue: 0,0:00:41.67,0:00:46.47,cloveroprom,,0,0,0,,{\fad(100,200)}aki ni nari mata fuyu ni nari hitotsu toshi wo totta
Dialogue: 0,0:00:47.10,0:00:53.26,cloveroprom,,0,0,0,,{\fad(100,200)}tooku made nigete iru tsumori demo owaranai kimi no story
Dialogue: 0,0:00:53.26,0:00:55.52,cloveroprom,,0,0,0,,{\fad(100,200)}niya niya waratte iru
Dialogue: 0,0:00:55.52,0:00:59.11,cloveroprom,,0,0,0,,{\fad(100,200)}fugainaiya iya
Dialogue: 0,0:00:59.11,0:01:05.25,cloveroprom,,0,0,0,,{\fad(100,200)}sugari nagara oikakete mitemo ashige ni saretemo
Dialogue: 0,0:01:05.25,0:01:07.44,cloveroprom,,0,0,0,,{\fad(100,200)}aita ana wo fusagou
Dialogue: 0,0:01:07.44,0:01:10.36,cloveroprom,,0,0,0,,{\fad(100,200)}chigai nai ya iya
Dialogue: 0,0:01:10.36,0:01:17.74,cloveroprom,,0,0,0,,{\fad(100,200)}fugainai ya iya
Dialogue: 0,0:01:19.33,0:01:28.36,cloveroprom,,0,0,0,,{\fad(100,200)}tsurai naa iya iya
Dialogue: 0,0:00:01.18,0:00:06.24,cloveropeng,,0,0,0,,{\fad(100,200)}My hometown lay buried in snow the morning I was born.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:07.07,0:00:11.78,cloveropeng,,0,0,0,,{\fad(100,200)}I looked up at the blue sky with my tiny hands.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:13.09,0:00:18.41,cloveropeng,,0,0,0,,{\fad(100,200)}The face of the girl next door that I've known so well...
Dialogue: 0,0:00:19.14,0:00:23.27,cloveropeng,,0,0,0,,{\fad(100,200)}It's as familiar as the graduation canon.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:23.27,0:00:29.23,cloveropeng,,0,0,0,,{\fad(100,200)}Thriving in solitude has been mistaken as my life story.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:29.23,0:00:31.51,cloveropeng,,0,0,0,,{\fad(100,200)}I want to blame it on someone.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:31.51,0:00:35.55,cloveropeng,,0,0,0,,{\fad(100,200)}It's so difficult. No, I hate it.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:35.55,0:00:41.05,cloveropeng,,0,0,0,,{\fad(100,200)}Tears and sorrow caused me to miss my chance.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:41.67,0:00:46.47,cloveropeng,,0,0,0,,{\fad(100,200)}Autumn passed, winter came again, and I became a year older.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:47.10,0:00:53.26,cloveropeng,,0,0,0,,{\fad(100,200)}You think you've run far away, but your story never ends.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:53.26,0:00:55.52,cloveropeng,,0,0,0,,{\fad(100,200)}And yet, you're smirking.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:55.52,0:00:59.11,cloveropeng,,0,0,0,,{\fad(100,200)}It's so cowardly. I hate it.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:59.11,0:01:05.25,cloveropeng,,0,0,0,,{\fad(100,200)}Even if I have to cling to you, chase after you, and get kicked down...
Dialogue: 0,0:01:05.25,0:01:07.44,cloveropeng,,0,0,0,,{\fad(100,200)}...I'll close the hole that's opened...
Dialogue: 0,0:01:07.44,0:01:10.36,cloveropeng,,0,0,0,,{\fad(100,200)}...without a doubt. No...
Dialogue: 0,0:01:10.36,0:01:17.74,cloveropeng,,0,0,0,,{\fad(100,200)}It's so cowardly. No...
Dialogue: 0,0:01:19.33,0:01:28.36,cloveropeng,,0,0,0,,{\fad(100,200)}It's so difficult. I hate it. I hate it.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:35.31,0:01:38.49,thoughts,,0,0,0,,I want to open all these boxes...
Dialogue: 0,0:01:40.13,0:01:45.66,thoughts,,0,0,0,,...but a mortal life span is too short to do such a thing.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:47.63,0:01:52.71,thoughts,,0,0,0,,A single lifetime limits how many boxes you can open.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:54.76,0:01:55.57,thoughts,,0,0,0,,But...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:29.78,0:02:30.58,clover,,0,0,0,,What's wrong?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:31.28,0:02:32.23,clover,,0,0,0,,My hand...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:33.25,0:02:34.45,clover,,0,0,0,,It's swollen.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:34.76,0:02:35.96,clover,,0,0,0,,It won't move.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:36.58,0:02:40.94,clover,,0,0,0,,At this rate, my hand will be paralyzed.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:41.42,0:02:43.96,clover,,0,0,0,,I need to go back... the hospital...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:43.96,0:02:45.28,clover,,0,0,0,,Shuu-chan!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:51.14,0:02:52.11,clover,,0,0,0,,I'm going back.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:52.50,0:02:53.74,clover,,0,0,0,,I need to go back.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:54.75,0:02:57.90,clover,,0,0,0,,O-Or else, my hand is going to die.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:58.93,0:03:00.78,clover,,0,0,0,,Anything but that...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:00.78,0:03:02.30,clover,,0,0,0,,I can't let that happen!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:03.01,0:03:05.55,clover,,0,0,0,,I'll die if I can't draw anymore!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:12.06,0:03:13.07,clover,,0,0,0,,I understand.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:22.65,0:03:33.90,cloverinsert,,0,0,0,,{\fad(100,200)}gaitou ga utsushidashita futari no kage wa yukkuri to\NOur shadows created by the street lights...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:35.09,0:03:46.49,cloverinsert,,0,0,0,,{\fad(100,200)}kimi no ie no hou e nobite hodo naku kieta\N...slowly moved toward your house and faded away.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:47.62,0:03:58.66,cloverinsert,,0,0,0,,{\fad(100,200)}ashita ni wa ii koto ga futari ni aru kanaa\NI wonder if tomorrow holds anything nice for us?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:59.00,0:04:11.03,cloverinsert,,0,0,0,,{\fad(100,200)}tokidoki subete wa kowarekakete kimi wa kotoba wo nakushite shimau\NSometimes, everything seems to break down and you don't know what to say.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:11.47,0:04:18.00,cloverinsert,,0,0,0,,{\fad(100,200)}boku de wa namida wo umaku nuguenai\NI can't wipe away your tears well enough.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:18.46,0:04:24.72,cloverinsert,,0,0,0,,{\fad(100,200)}kaeri no michi kage wa hitotsu dake\NOnly one shadow leaves your house.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:31.11,0:04:42.68,cloverinsert,,0,0,0,,{\fad(100,200)}saishuu no chikatetsu wa dareka no jiko de konde ite\NThe last subway train of the night was delayed because of an accident.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:43.63,0:04:54.98,cloverinsert,,0,0,0,,{\fad(100,200)}hitonami ni osarete bonyari tokei wo mite ita\NPushed around by the crowds, I was staring blankly at my watch.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:56.16,0:05:07.24,cloverinsert,,0,0,0,,{\fad(100,200)}ashita made ato sukoshi nanika ga kawarukanaa\NI wonder if anything will change tomorrow?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:07.58,0:05:19.67,cloverinsert,,0,0,0,,{\fad(100,200)}bokura ga umarete kieru aida doredake hito wo sukueru darou\NHow many people can we help in our lifetimes?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:19.99,0:05:26.68,cloverinsert,,0,0,0,,{\fad(100,200)}yogoreta mado ni wa nani mo utsuranai\NI can't see anything outside the dirty train window.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:27.07,0:05:33.41,cloverinsert,,0,0,0,,{\fad(100,200)}kimi wa mou nemutte shimattan darou ka na\NI wonder if you've gone to sleep already?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:47.49,0:05:48.20,clover,,0,0,0,,How's your hand?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:48.57,0:05:49.90,clover,,0,0,0,,It's all right now.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:50.55,0:05:53.12,clover,,0,0,0,,I'm sorry for scaring you like that.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:54.48,0:05:56.51,clover,,0,0,0,,What happened to your cheek?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:58.99,0:06:00.48,clover,,0,0,0,,Sensei punched me.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:01.30,0:06:03.47,clover,,0,0,0,,But I returned it to him threefold!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:04.53,0:06:07.02,clover,,0,0,0,,It's all right. It just so happens we're at a hospital!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:09.15,0:06:10.30,clover,,0,0,0,,I'm sorry.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:11.23,0:06:12.99,clover,,0,0,0,,Why do you need to apologize?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:20.45,0:06:21.59,clover,,0,0,0,,I see.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:23.67,0:06:25.97,clover,,0,0,0,,So you've decided.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:29.63,0:06:31.77,clover,,0,0,0,,Please watch me. I'll get better.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:32.12,0:06:33.76,clover,,0,0,0,,I'll definitely get better.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:34.31,0:06:39.20,clover,,0,0,0,,Actually, it's okay if I don't get better and can't leave my mark.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:39.96,0:06:42.83,clover,,0,0,0,,I understand now that I really want to draw.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:43.29,0:06:47.56,clover,,0,0,0,,There's no other life for me.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:49.71,0:06:53.28,clover,,0,0,0,,What you told me last night really made me happy.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:53.74,0:06:55.11,clover,,0,0,0,,I won't forget it.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:55.51,0:06:58.98,clover,,0,0,0,,I'll always be watching you.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:01.12,0:07:05.44,clover,,0,0,0,,If you find your brother, make sure you catch him and tell him...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:07.75,0:07:13.78,clover,,0,0,0,,...strongly and clearly, the same words that you told me last night.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:18.80,0:07:21.81,clover,,0,0,0,,Sensei will kill you if he finds you.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:27.64,0:07:28.98,clover,,0,0,0,,He already slugged me.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:31.47,0:07:35.28,clover,,0,0,0,,Yeah... but I returned to him fourfold.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:36.62,0:07:41.70,clover,,0,0,0,,Sheesh... I should've punched him more than just four times as much...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:47.99,0:07:49.06,clover,,0,0,0,,Morita-san...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:50.87,0:07:52.21,clover,,0,0,0,,Please get on.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:02.45,0:08:04.31,clover,,0,0,0,,Does she know about this?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:05.02,0:08:06.77,clover,,0,0,0,,He told me not to tell her.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:07.43,0:08:09.80,clover,,0,0,0,,That he wants her to decide without knowing about this.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:09.80,0:08:11.10,clover,,0,0,0,,I see...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:11.82,0:08:16.06,clover,,0,0,0,,So that geezer's finally going all out.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:17.35,0:08:19.66,thoughts,,0,0,0,,Isn't it your duty to care for her?!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:21.87,0:08:23.45,clover,,0,0,0,,Sacrificing everything?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:25.58,0:08:28.05,clover,,0,0,0,,Damn... I can't beat that...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:54.62,0:08:57.15,clover,,0,0,0,,There's no going back...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:57.81,0:09:00.42,clover,,0,0,0,,Truly, never again.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:05.29,0:09:07.46,clover,,0,0,0,,Ouch...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:10.88,0:09:13.31,clover,,0,0,0,,Well then...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:21.90,0:09:23.97,clover,,0,0,0,,Hagu, how's your hand?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:25.57,0:09:27.04,clover,,0,0,0,,Shuu-chan...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:34.17,0:09:35.26,clover,,0,0,0,,Um, Hagu...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:35.26,0:09:36.44,clover,,0,0,0,,Shuu-chan...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:37.39,0:09:38.82,clover,,0,0,0,,Will you hold my hand?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:39.93,0:09:40.86,clover,,0,0,0,,S-Sure.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:44.87,0:09:47.79,clover,,0,0,0,,Um, I have a request for you.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:50.92,0:09:54.50,clover,,0,0,0,,Please give me your life, Shuu-chan.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:56.72,0:09:59.61,clover,,0,0,0,,I'm sorry for asking this of you when I don't know if I can give anything back in return...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:59.95,0:10:01.53,clover,,0,0,0,,And for saying something like this...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:02.02,0:10:02.97,clover,,0,0,0,,But...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:03.66,0:10:08.76,clover,,0,0,0,,But I want to draw... for the rest of my life.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:09.79,0:10:14.45,clover,,0,0,0,,So please stay with me... until the very, very end.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:19.65,0:10:20.80,clover,,0,0,0,,Shuu-chan?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:21.66,0:10:23.58,clover,,0,0,0,,I-I'm sorry.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:24.33,0:10:26.62,clover,,0,0,0,,W-Was that too much to ask?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:33.72,0:10:34.64,clover,,0,0,0,,Sure.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:35.55,0:10:37.15,clover,,0,0,0,,You don't need to give me anything in return.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:41.08,0:10:42.22,clover,,0,0,0,,I'll give you everything.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:56.24,0:10:57.62,thoughts,,0,0,0,,I love the rain.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:58.69,0:11:01.53,thoughts,,0,0,0,,The borders of the world become blurred...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:02.63,0:11:05.52,thoughts,,0,0,0,,...and it feels like I'm about to get sucked in.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:14.72,0:11:16.44,clover,,0,0,0,,Hello!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:17.30,0:11:21.36,clover,,0,0,0,,See, it's Hagu-chan!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:21.36,0:11:24.57,clover,,0,0,0,,Shuuji is back from Tokyo!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:24.57,0:11:25.84,clover,,0,0,0,,Try going to his room.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:48.18,0:11:50.55,thoughts,,0,0,0,,I loved Shuu-chan's room.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:52.78,0:11:54.14,thoughts,,0,0,0,,The scent of books...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:56.19,0:11:59.56,thoughts,,0,0,0,,His sketchbooks and his shelves with paint marks...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:05.76,0:12:07.61,thoughts,,0,0,0,,I love the sound of rain.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:08.78,0:12:10.43,thoughts,,0,0,0,,It really soothes me.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:11.10,0:12:14.94,thoughts,,0,0,0,,It's as if it's gently healing everything...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:16.03,0:12:20.63,thoughts,,0,0,0,,The mountain, the trees, the grass, the roof...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:23.32,0:12:25.68,thoughts,,0,0,0,,And me...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:33.92,0:12:37.71,clover,,0,0,0,,Hagu-chan! Shuuji! I sliced up some watermelon.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:37.71,0:12:39.21,clover,,0,0,0,,Why don't you come eat some?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:40.23,0:12:44.06,clover,,0,0,0,,Oh, goodness, they get along so well.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:45.51,0:12:49.91,thoughts,,0,0,0,,That's it. Shuu-chan is like the rain.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:57.17,0:12:58.80,thoughts,,0,0,0,,What's wrong, Hagu?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:00.97,0:13:03.76,thoughts,,0,0,0,,Shuu-chan is like the rain.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:05.64,0:13:08.30,thoughts,,0,0,0,,Just seeing him relieves me.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:09.71,0:13:11.58,thoughts,,0,0,0,,So much that it makes me want to cry.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:14.18,0:13:18.81,thoughts,,0,0,0,,He always came looking for me when I got lost.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:23.20,0:13:23.98,thoughts,,0,0,0,,Let's go.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:27.49,0:13:31.32,thoughts,,0,0,0,,He always gently reached out to me.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:35.74,0:13:38.02,thoughts,,0,0,0,,Hagu, let's make you get better.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:39.25,0:13:44.93,thoughts,,0,0,0,,Your talents aren't something to be wasted so easily.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:46.94,0:13:48.45,thoughts,,0,0,0,,Don't think that you're alone.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:48.93,0:13:50.36,thoughts,,0,0,0,,I'm with you.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:51.55,0:13:55.96,thoughts,,0,0,0,,That's right, Shuu-chan must be my rain.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:57.29,0:14:00.29,thoughts,,0,0,0,,Being with him makes me breathe deeply...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:01.81,0:14:06.25,thoughts,,0,0,0,,...and it gives me the feeling that I can grow bigger and bigger like the trees and the grass.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:09.88,0:14:13.40,thoughts,,0,0,0,,This person who always smiles at me with a slightly troubled look on his face...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:14.87,0:14:16.76,thoughts,,0,0,0,,He's very...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:19.03,0:14:20.48,thoughts,,0,0,0,,...precious to me.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:43.34,0:14:44.61,clover,,0,0,0,,My body hurts!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:45.19,0:14:47.79,clover,,0,0,0,,It's so cold, Takemoto!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:47.79,0:14:49.95,clover,,0,0,0,,Warm me up. Hold me tight!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:52.70,0:14:57.03,clover,,0,0,0,,Hey, Takemoto, is this dawn or dusk...?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:57.03,0:15:00.70,clover,,0,0,0,,Well, the clock says five o'clock.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:00.70,0:15:01.52,clover,,0,0,0,,Five o'clock?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:01.52,0:15:02.43,clover,,0,0,0,,Which five o'clock?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:06.18,0:15:09.15,clover,,0,0,0,,Why don't we go eat something? I'll pay.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:11.13,0:15:14.68,clover,,0,0,0,,So bright...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:15.67,0:15:19.66,clover,,0,0,0,,Why does the river have to shine so brightly?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:19.66,0:15:23.18,clover,,0,0,0,,I-It's so shiny it's offensive...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:23.18,0:15:25.94,clover,,0,0,0,,...and it's all glittering like there's a layer of oil on the surface.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:25.94,0:15:27.92,clover,,0,0,0,,It must be morning.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:27.92,0:15:30.92,clover,,0,0,0,,This brilliance is unmistakably that of morning.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:30.92,0:15:33.51,clover,,0,0,0,,Only the convenience store was open, too.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:35.36,0:15:37.76,clover,,0,0,0,,What the hell? You have a cold?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:37.76,0:15:39.35,clover,,0,0,0,,Don't sneeze like that when you're upwind of me!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:39.35,0:15:41.60,clover,,0,0,0,,What if my precious self caught it?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:41.60,0:15:43.70,clover,,0,0,0,,Yeah, yeah, so sorry.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:43.70,0:15:48.39,clover,,0,0,0,,We fell asleep without a futon or anything. Of course I'd catch a cold.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:48.74,0:15:50.05,clover,,0,0,0,,Or rather, can't you worry about me a little...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:51.18,0:15:54.28,clover,,0,0,0,,That grilled pepper garlic sausage is mine!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:54.28,0:15:56.99,clover,,0,0,0,,Why the hell are you eating it, ya damn punk?!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:56.99,0:15:58.92,clover,,0,0,0,,Why, you...!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:57.72,0:15:58.92,clover,,0,0,0,,Yeah, yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:58.92,0:16:00.63,clover,,0,0,0,,Give it back!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:59.14,0:16:02.43,clover,,0,0,0,,Sure, I'll give it back.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:00.63,0:16:02.43,clover,,0,0,0,,Give it back{\fscx200}-{\r}!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:04.98,0:16:09.33,clover,,0,0,0,,Sheesh... Hagu-chan was right for not picking a guy like him.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:09.33,0:16:11.00,clover,,0,0,0,,What?!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:11.38,0:16:14.06,clover,,0,0,0,,What did you just say?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:14.06,0:16:17.91,clover,,0,0,0,,I'm saying that Hagu-chan was right in picking Sensei.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:17.91,0:16:19.21,clover,,0,0,0,,What the hell?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:19.21,0:16:21.64,clover,,0,0,0,,What are you saying, acting like you know everything?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:21.64,0:16:22.68,clover,,0,0,0,,Aren't you bitter?!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:22.96,0:16:24.51,clover,,0,0,0,,Yeah, I'm bitter!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:24.51,0:16:26.58,clover,,0,0,0,,I've been thinking a lot about it, too!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:27.11,0:16:31.55,clover,,0,0,0,,But no matter how much I thought about it, you and I can't make her happy...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:31.55,0:16:32.85,clover,,0,0,0,,...only Sensei can!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:45.50,0:16:48.34,clover,,0,0,0,,Damn it, you're the last person I want to hear that from!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:48.34,0:16:51.00,clover,,0,0,0,,She rejected you ages ago!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:51.00,0:16:52.72,clover,,0,0,0,,Yeah, she did!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:52.72,0:16:54.25,clover,,0,0,0,,She rejected me, so what?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:57.69,0:17:00.97,clover,,0,0,0,,Actually you know what? I'm so glad you got rejected, too!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:01.83,0:17:05.31,clover,,0,0,0,,I didn't want you taking her from me!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:06.01,0:17:07.02,clover,,0,0,0,,What did you say...?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:07.79,0:17:11.23,clover,,0,0,0,,You fourth-degree self-realizer! Unskilled amateur! Pauper!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:12.23,0:17:16.13,clover,,0,0,0,,Yeah, I don't have anything! Money nor talent!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:16.54,0:17:20.51,clover,,0,0,0,,I'm really glad Hagu-chan chose Sensei!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:21.00,0:17:22.40,clover,,0,0,0,,If I was going to lose...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:22.40,0:17:29.08,clover,,0,0,0,,...I'd much rather lose to compassion and honor than money and talent!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:29.08,0:17:30.45,thoughts,,0,0,0,,Talent?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:30.95,0:17:32.29,thoughts,,0,0,0,,Talent, did you say?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:33.74,0:17:35.23,thoughts,,0,0,0,,What talent?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:40.95,0:17:42.16,thoughts,,0,0,0,,Talent...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:44.87,0:17:49.98,thoughts,,0,0,0,,Everyone arbitrarily loves, hates, and curses others for that.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:50.83,0:17:52.88,thoughts,,0,0,0,,And in the end, they all quietly drift away.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:55.81,0:17:57.32,thoughts,,0,0,0,,It was sad.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:57.86,0:18:00.92,thoughts,,0,0,0,,I wanted everything to end.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:04.38,0:18:06.63,thoughts,,0,0,0,,That's why I tried to drag her down with me.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:08.38,0:18:09.41,thoughts,,0,0,0,,I know.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:10.25,0:18:11.76,thoughts,,0,0,0,,I looked to her as an escape...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:12.49,0:18:14.40,thoughts,,0,0,0,,When she was so damaged herself...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:16.86,0:18:18.33,thoughts,,0,0,0,,I'm the worst.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:19.55,0:18:23.30,clover,,0,0,0,,So you're saying that geezer could make her happier?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:25.18,0:18:29.64,clover,,0,0,0,,I knew that, too, from the very beginning!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:29.87,0:18:31.21,clover,,0,0,0,,Then...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:31.21,0:18:33.22,clover,,0,0,0,,But you know what? I...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:39.72,0:18:43.32,dog,,0,0,0,,{\fad(568,0)\c&H303035&\an1}Let me in!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:39.72,0:18:43.32,dog,,0,0,0,,{\fad(568,0)\c&H303035&\pos(287,418)}Takemoto's leg
Dialogue: 0,0:18:39.72,0:18:43.32,dog,,0,0,0,,{\fad(568,0)\c&H303035&\pos(425,48)}Morita's leg
Dialogue: 0,0:18:39.72,0:18:43.32,dog,,0,0,0,,{\fad(568,0)\an3\c&H303035&}A fight?\NAre you guys fighting?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:46.56,0:18:51.48,dog,,0,0,0,,{\c&HC8EAE8&\3c&H75958E&\pos(358,292)\fad(443,0)}two young men
Dialogue: 0,0:18:47.31,0:18:51.48,dog,,0,0,0,,{\pos(117,48)\frz15.593\fad(568,0)\c&HE79280&\3c&H75554D&}blue sky
Dialogue: 0,0:18:47.94,0:18:51.48,dog,,0,0,0,,{\fad(439,0)\frz329.209\pos(638,69)\c&H91CA6B&\3c&H51673A&}wind
Dialogue: 0,0:18:48.56,0:18:51.48,dog,,0,0,0,,{\fad(445,0)\c&H5682E9&\3c&H2E616F&\pos(489,375)}river embankment
Dialogue: 0,0:18:53.53,0:18:55.69,sign,,0,0,0,,{\bord2.5\fad(480,0)\pos(412,238)\c&H4D4EB0&\fs48\frz3.581\3c&H303738&}adolescence
Dialogue: 0,0:18:58.39,0:19:01.67,clover,,0,0,0,,M-Man, today's sparring sure was heated.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:01.67,0:19:04.33,clover,,0,0,0,,T-The national tournament is soon, after all!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:04.33,0:19:05.84,clover,,0,0,0,,It really gets you pumped up, huh?!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:05.84,0:19:06.68,clover,,0,0,0,,No doubt about it!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:07.10,0:19:09.85,clover,,0,0,0,,Well then, why don't we get back to school?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:09.85,0:19:13.51,clover,,0,0,0,,Yeah, why don't we do that soon?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:14.04,0:19:18.10,clover,,0,0,0,,That's great... it reminds me of the old days...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:18.10,0:19:23.40,clover,,0,0,0,,You look great even in a fist fight... it's like it was when I was young.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:29.34,0:19:33.35,clover,,0,0,0,,I fell asleep sitting in a chair, so my shoulders and back...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:36.79,0:19:38.44,clover,,0,0,0,,Is someone there?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:38.44,0:19:42.04,clover,,0,0,0,,Huh, what's this box?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:42.34,0:19:45.30,sign,,0,0,0,,Help her get better no matter what
Dialogue: 0,0:19:48.70,0:19:49.81,clover,,0,0,0,,Morita...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:55.73,0:19:56.92,clover,,0,0,0,,Morita!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:01.72,0:20:02.91,clover,,0,0,0,,Heave-ho!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:06.72,0:20:08.98,clover,,0,0,0,,Hey, wait a second... this is for...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:08.98,0:20:12.28,clover,,0,0,0,,I really appreciate it! I'll make good use of it!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:12.28,0:20:14.23,clover,,0,0,0,,But this is enough!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:14.23,0:20:16.67,clover,,0,0,0,,And I'll be sure to pay you back!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:17.14,0:20:20.02,clover,,0,0,0,,I'll return the money but not Hagu though!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:22.19,0:20:24.37,clover,,0,0,0,,Don't you dare think that this is the end!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:24.37,0:20:25.95,clover,,0,0,0,,Don't forget about that!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:26.37,0:20:28.59,clover,,0,0,0,,Yeah, I'll remember it.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:29.35,0:20:31.18,clover,,0,0,0,,I'll definitely help her get better...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:31.18,0:20:33.62,clover,,0,0,0,,...and she'll definitely be able to draw again.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:33.95,0:20:34.77,clover,,0,0,0,,So don't worry about it.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:37.41,0:20:40.15,clover,,0,0,0,,Hey, you... do you love her?!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:43.40,0:20:44.49,clover,,0,0,0,,Yeah!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:44.49,0:20:45.53,clover,,0,0,0,,I love her!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:45.53,0:20:46.76,clover,,0,0,0,,I love her very much!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:51.66,0:20:53.06,clover,,0,0,0,,What did he say?!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:53.06,0:20:54.76,clover,,0,0,0,,It's adolescence!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:53.52,0:20:55.69,clover,,0,0,0,,I never knew, Hanamoto-kun!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:54.76,0:20:57.18,clover,,0,0,0,,Lord Adolescence has arrived!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:55.69,0:20:57.84,clover,,0,0,0,,What? Hanamoto-sensei?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:57.84,0:21:01.44,clover,,0,0,0,,Bring sake! Someone, bring some sake!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:57.84,0:21:01.15,clover,,0,0,0,,No way?! It never seemed that way...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:01.86,0:21:05.08,thoughts,,0,0,0,,A toast to Lord Adolescence!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:04.21,0:21:10.50,thoughts,,0,0,0,,Heave-ho! Heave-ho! Heave-ho!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:05.08,0:21:08.29,thoughts,,0,0,0,,Cheers for Hanamoto-kun!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:10.50,0:21:11.82,clover,,0,0,0,,I won't forget.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:12.46,0:21:15.56,clover,,0,0,0,,And I'll watch you forever.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:16.43,0:21:19.19,clover,,0,0,0,,Forever and ever...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:20.67,0:21:29.81,cloveredrom,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,300)}arifurete iru kimochi nante sa
Dialogue: 0,0:21:20.67,0:21:29.81,cloveredeng,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,300)}It would be so much easier...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:32.17,0:21:40.27,cloveredrom,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,0)}nanimo iwazu ni isso kieteshimaeba
Dialogue: 0,0:21:32.17,0:21:40.27,cloveredeng,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,0)}...if these stale emotions...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:40.27,0:21:43.69,cloveredrom,,0,0,0,,raku ni nareru no ni
Dialogue: 0,0:21:40.27,0:21:43.69,cloveredeng,,0,0,0,,...could just disappear without a word.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:43.69,0:21:52.82,cloveredrom,,0,0,0,,{\fad(0,300)}sorezore no michi wo yuku sono wakaremichi
Dialogue: 0,0:21:43.69,0:21:52.82,cloveredeng,,0,0,0,,{\fad(0,300)}At the crossroads where we split ways...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:55.37,0:22:06.30,cloveredrom,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,0)}mou nidoto au koto no nai deai wa kanashisugiru
Dialogue: 0,0:21:55.37,0:22:06.30,cloveredeng,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,0)}...it saddens me to think we may never meet again.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:06.30,0:22:09.04,cloveredrom,,0,0,0,,tarinai kimochi wo mochiyotte
Dialogue: 0,0:22:06.30,0:22:09.04,cloveredeng,,0,0,0,,Despite adding the emotions that are lacking...
Dialogue: 0,0:22:09.04,0:22:11.90,cloveredrom,,0,0,0,,atatameta saki kara hieteitte
Dialogue: 0,0:22:09.04,0:22:11.90,cloveredeng,,0,0,0,,...things cool off just as soon as I warm them...
Dialogue: 0,0:22:11.90,0:22:16.24,cloveredrom,,0,0,0,,{\fad(0,300)}sonna hazu naitte shinjiteru
Dialogue: 0,0:22:11.90,0:22:16.24,cloveredeng,,0,0,0,,{\fad(0,300)}...but I still don't want to believe.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:17.61,0:22:24.94,cloveredrom,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,0)}ittai itsumade onaji kotoba wo kakaekondenda
Dialogue: 0,0:22:17.61,0:22:24.94,cloveredeng,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,0)}Just how long am I going to brood over the same word?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:24.94,0:22:28.34,cloveredrom,,0,0,0,,{\fad(0,300)}kakekondenda
Dialogue: 0,0:22:24.94,0:22:28.34,cloveredeng,,0,0,0,,{\fad(0,300)}How long...?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:30.90,0:22:34.49,clover,,0,0,0,,Next episode: With Honey and Clover.
